<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1323 gunēṁṭi cai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tra śuddha trayōdaśi sōmavāramunāṁḍu bobbili
<lb n="3"/>nelavīṭi saliseṭi koḍuku kēsisēnāpati tanakunu Abhī
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṣṭārtthasiddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhyanādhunikini nityamu
<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>nnu</unclear> modaṭi dhupaAvasarananu catanu Oka doṁḍa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vanamāla samarppiṁcenu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Iṁdulakunu puṣpa<unclear>vāṭi</unclear>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ka gaṭlu reṁḍu vilici bhumiAnnamavaśāna peṭenu
<lb n="8"/>Ītanikini prasādamu reṁḍu guṁcalu padi
<lb n="9"/>maḍalaku ṭāvupaṭi peṭenu Ītaṁḍu Īpra
<lb n="10" break="no"/>sadamu bhujiṁci I doṁḍavanamāla Āca
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṁdrarkkasthāIgāṁ deci peṭadivāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I dha
<lb n="12"/>rmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

